#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/ma/extras.py:docstring
#: of numpy.ma.extras.vander:29
msgid ""
"Vandermonde matrix.  If `increasing` is False, the first column is "
"``x^(N-1)``, the second ``x^(N-2)`` and so forth. If `increasing` is True, "
"the columns are ``x^0, x^1, ..., x^(N-1)``."
msgstr ""

